            . - Mr. Gleed. You live, I belive, with Messrs. Creaton and sons, who are auctioneers. - A. Yes.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you know these premises and the buildings that were purchased by Mr. White and Tucker. - A. Yes.</p>
               <p>Q. Were you ever upon these premises when 
               <persName id="t18071028-43-person534">
                  Jacob 
                  Joseph
               <interp inst="t18071028-43-person534" type="surname" value="Joseph"></interp>
